Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:21.04,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ここはきっと儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:23.73,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}目指して
